Package com.innowhere.jnieasy.core.data

Provides the interfaces to be implemented by native capable classes, user defined or predefined, with the exception of interfaces related to methods.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
CanBeNativeCapable The CanBeNativeCapable is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of "can be native" objects (String, Integer, Java arrays etc).
CanBeNativeCapableArray The CanBeNativeCapableArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of "can be native" object arrays (String[], Integer[], int[][] etc).
CPPClass The CPPClass is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as C++ classes.
NativeArray The NativeArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of arrays (String[], MyStructure[], int[], int[][] etc).
NativeArrayOfArray The NativeArrayOfArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping multidimensional native arrays.
NativeBoolean The NativeBoolean is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping a boolean value.
NativeBooleanArray The NativeBooleanArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping one-dimensional native arrays of boolean.
NativeBooleanObject The NativeBooleanObject is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of java.lang.Boolean objects.
NativeBooleanObjectArray The NativeBooleanObjectArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping one-dimensional native arrays of java.lang.Boolean.
NativeByte The NativeByte is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping a byte value.
NativeByteArray The NativeByteArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping one-dimensional native arrays of byte.
NativeByteObject The NativeByteObject is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of java.lang.Byte objects.
NativeByteObjectArray The NativeByteObjectArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping one-dimensional native arrays of java.lang.Byte.
NativeCapable The NativeCapable is the interface implemented by all native capable classes.
NativeCapableArray The NativeCapableArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of native capable object arrays (MyStructure[], Pointer[] etc).
NativeCharacter The NativeCharacter is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping a char value.
NativeCharacterArray The NativeCharacterArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping one-dimensional native arrays of character.
NativeCharacterObject The NativeCharacterObject is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of java.lang.Character objects.
NativeCharacterObjectArray The NativeCharacterObjectArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping one-dimensional native arrays of java.lang.Character.
NativeDouble The NativeDouble is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping a double value.
NativeDoubleArray The NativeDoubleArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping one-dimensional native arrays of double.
NativeDoubleObject The NativeDoubleObject is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of java.lang.Double objects.
NativeDoubleObjectArray The NativeDoubleObjectArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping one-dimensional native arrays of java.lang.Double.
NativeFieldContainer The NativeFieldContainer is the interface implemented by native capable classes containing fields.
NativeFloat The NativeFloat is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping a float value.
NativeFloatArray The NativeFloatArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping one-dimensional native arrays of float.
NativeFloatObject The NativeFloatObject is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of java.lang.Float objects.
NativeFloatObjectArray The NativeFloatObjectArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping one-dimensional native arrays of java.lang.Float.
NativeInteger The NativeInteger is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping an int value.
NativeIntegerArray The NativeIntegerArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping one-dimensional native arrays of integer.
NativeIntegerObject The NativeIntegerObject is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of java.lang.Integer objects.
NativeIntegerObjectArray The NativeIntegerObjectArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping one-dimensional native arrays of java.lang.Integer.
NativeLong The NativeLong is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping a long value.
NativeLongArray The NativeLongArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping one-dimensional native arrays of long.
NativeLongObject The NativeLongObject is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of java.lang.Long objects.
NativeLongObjectArray The NativeLongObjectArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping one-dimensional native arrays of java.lang.Long.
NativeMemberReflection The NativeMemberReflection is the interface implemented by native capable classes that make accessible fields and methods from native using Java reflection.
NativeMemberReflectionArray The NativeMemberReflectionArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of one-dimensional reflection object arrays (Field[], Method[], Constructor[]).
NativeMultipleFieldContainer The NativeMultipleFieldContainer is the interface implemented by native capable classes containing multiple fields like unions, structures and C++ classes.
NativeNumber The NativeNumber is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping primitive number values.
NativeNumberArray The NativeNumberArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping one-dimensional native arrays of primitive number types.
NativeNumberObject The NativeNumberObject is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of inherited java.lang.Number objects.
NativeNumberObjectArray The NativeNumberObjectArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of primitive number wrapper object arrays (Float[], Integer[] etc).
NativeObjectArray The NativeObjectArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of object arrays (String[], MyStructure[], int[][] etc).
NativeObjectFieldContainer The NativeObjectFieldContainer is the interface implemented by native capable classes containing only one Object native field.
NativePointer The NativePointer is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping a native object reference working as a native pointer.
NativePrimitive The NativePrimitive is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping primitive values.
NativePrimitiveArray The NativePrimitiveArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping one-dimensional native arrays of primitive types.
NativePrimitiveObject The NumberObject is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of inherited java.lang.Number, java.lang.Character and java.lang.Boolean objects.
NativePrimitiveObjectArray The NativePrimitiveObjectArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of primitive wrapper object arrays (Boolean[], Integer[] etc).
NativeSeparatedFieldContainer The NativeSeparatedFieldContainer is the interface implemented by native capable classes containing separated multiple native fields like structures and C++ classes (not unions).
NativeShort The NativeShort is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping a short value.
NativeShortArray The NativeShortArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping one-dimensional native arrays of short.
NativeShortObject The NativeShortObject is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of java.lang.Short objects.
NativeShortObjectArray The NativeShortObjectArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping one-dimensional native arrays of java.lang.Short.
NativeSingleFieldContainer The NativeSingleFieldContainer is the interface implemented by native capable classes containing only one Object native field.
NativeString The NativeString is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of java.lang.String objects.
NativeStringAnsi The NativeStringAnsi is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of java.lang.String objects with ANSI encoding/size in native memory.
NativeStringAnsiArray The NativeStringAnsiArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of java.lang.String arrays (String[]) using ANSI encoding/size.
NativeStringArray The NativeStringArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of java.lang.String arrays (String[]).
NativeStringBased The NativeStringBased is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of string objects: String and StringBuffer.
NativeStringBuffer The NativeStringBuffer is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of java.lang.StringBuffer objects.
NativeStringBufferAnsi The NativeStringBufferAnsi is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of java.lang.StringBuffer objects with ANSI encoding/size in native memory.
NativeStringBufferAnsiArray The NativeStringBufferAnsiArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of java.lang.StringBuffer arrays (StringBuffer[]) using ANSI encoding/size.
NativeStringBufferArray The NativeStringBufferArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of java.lang.StringBuffer arrays (StringBuffer[]).
NativeStringBufferUnicode The NativeStringBufferUnicode is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of java.lang.StringBuffer objects with UNICODE encoding/size in native memory.
NativeStringBufferUnicodeArray The NativeStringBufferUnicodeArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of java.lang.StringBuffer arrays (StringBuffer[]) using UNICODE encoding/size.
NativeStringUnicode The NativeStringUnicode is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of java.lang.String objects with UNICODE encoding/size in native memory.
NativeStringUnicodeArray The NativeStringUnicodeArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of java.lang.String arrays (String[]) using UNICODE encoding/size.
NativeUserDefinedClass The NativeUserDefinedClass is the interface implemented by all user defined native capable classes.
Structure The Structure is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as C structures.
Union The Structure is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as C unions.
 

Package com.innowhere.jnieasy.core.data Description

Provides the interfaces to be implemented by native capable classes, user defined or predefined, with the exception of interfaces related to methods.
